section.p:
Also, turn in solutions to these exercises: 


Write the following elements of S_5 as a product of disjoint cycles.



\alpha=\left(
					\begin{array}{ccccc}
					 1 & 2 & 3 & 4 & 5 \\
					 2 & 4 & 1 & 5 & 3 \\
					\end{array}
					\right)



\beta=\left(
					\begin{array}{ccccc}
					 1 & 2 & 3 & 4 & 5 \\
					 4 & 2 & 5 & 1 & 3 \\
					\end{array}
					\right)





Compute the following using the values of \alpha and \beta above.  Write your answer as a product of disjoint cycles.



\alpha \circ \beta


\beta \circ \alpha


\alpha^{-1}


\beta^{-1}
